name: 1st Edition Tezos Glaceon --CryptoMon Series
description: The buyer will receive a High Quality 1st Edition copy of the digital card. Every first edition has 2 available copies. One on Kalamint and another on Hic Et Nunc. The CryptoMon series is a new series of crypto inspired parody collectibles. There will be many more great Mons coming in the future all with 1st edition/Unlimited runs, as well as a few planned special editions. The set is currently planned to be 64 cards with secret rare cards available like a real Pokémon set (ex. 65/64). I hope you like the series!
